➜冈拉克发出警告，美元或将贬值20%！这一货币成新避险资产
http://www.sohu.com/a/432449475_334198	34383
<p class="ql-align-center" style="text-align: center;"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20201117/ba4e8e3d07c6431fb8134519a5acb1be.png" max-width="600"> </img></p>
